text: Rachel Fleet (n√©e Mason, born Amanda Fenshaw) is a fictional character from the BBC One school-based drama series Waterloo Road, portrayed by Eva Pope. Rachel first appeared in the seventh episode of the third series, first broadcast on 22 November 2007. She appeared as a regular character for nearly three years before departing in the series five finale, broadcast on 15 July 2010. Rachel appeared in 52 episodes in total.
